Interface FloatArrayFS

All Superinterfaces:
CommonArrayFS, FeatureStructure
All Known Implementing Classes:
FloatArray
public interface FloatArrayFS
extends CommonArrayFS

Interface for CAS float arrays. To create a float array object, use CAS.createFloatArrayFS().
